      Aggregator that sums up all the data points,and uses interpolation where previous value is used for data point missing.
      static Aggregator Aggregators.SQUARESUM
      Aggregator that returns the square sum of the data point.
      static Aggregator Aggregators.SUM
      Aggregator that sums up all the data points.
      static Aggregator Aggregators.ZIMSUM
      Sums data points but will cause the SpanGroup to return a 0 if timestamps don't line up instead of interpolating.
